text: Skärholmen is a borough (stadsdelsområde) of Söderort in the southern part of Stockholm. ==Overview== It is primarily made up of Skärholmen parish. The districts that make up the borough are Bredäng, Skärholmen, Sätra and Vårberg. The population is 33,662 on an area of 8.86 km², which gives a density of 3,800/km². ==References== ==External links== Category:Boroughs of Stockholm
